<br>
“Has the prince met the sorceress?” Alison asked. Whitney scoffed.<br>
<br>
“Of course not,” he answered. Pete smiled.<br>
<br>
“Well, as long as you keep that from happening, you shouldn’t have a problem,” Pete said. He was consumed with a happy feeling. Pete never liked the idea of Chloe and Lex being together on his own world, and if he had a chance to keep it from happening here, he was all for it.<br>
<br>
