<br>
“We’re not leaving,” she said. “I already called Clark and explained what was going on. He actually believes me.” Lex’s face fell as the words came out of Chloe’s mouth. Of course she had already called Clark. Now he just had to steal one of Alex’s cars and get Chloe and himself the hell out of town before she could meet up with him.<br>
<br>
