<br>
“You’re still not going to tell me, are you?” She asked. “I won’t tell anyone else if that’s what you’re worried about.” He eyed her as he contemplated his situation. The odds were that she’d find out anyway, since they were going to be living under the same roof as his double. He closed his eyes and nodded.<br>
<br>
