<br>
“It doesn’t matter,” he repeated. “Let me make love to you,” he whispered. Chloe’s breath hitched as she felt Clark’s naked form against hers. “Let me make love to my wife.” He didn’t wait for a response and moved his mouth down her body. Chloe looked at him warily.<br>
<br>
