<br>
“She doesn’t have a fever,” she whispered to the other women in the room. “I don’t understand what’s wrong with her.” Chloe started coughing, her whole body jerking with the movement, and blood came spraying out of her mouth. “Oh, God. What do we do?” The other woman shook her head.<br>
<br>
