<br>
“I don’t see any other choice without the king here,” she agreed. The two women started toward the door and the first woman turned back. “Have you seen the way he looks at her? If she dies then so do we.” The second woman nodded in agreement.<br>
<br>
“So does everyone else who was supposed to be taking care of her in his absence.”<br>
